Issues.Body:
Fixes #4969 

Main PR <!-- Link to PR if any that fixed this in the main branch. -->

## Description

When control `Name` property set null or bingind value is null, it will skip use `AntiFormat`.
Becaues input null string will throw NullReferenceException  in

https://github.com/dotnet/wpf/blob/6d1ec561f9d259974ce9ae45f917309649181252/src/Microsoft.DotNet.Wpf/src/WindowsBase/MS/Internal/AvTrace.cs#L405

## Customer Impact

When set `Name` property `null` or binding value is `null`, in debug mode set an error binding, vs will throw `NullReferenceException` in any wpf version(include .net 472, .net5.0-window and more)

## Regression

No

## Testing

Built and run this code
```csharp
 var t = new TextBox()
  {
      Name = null, // Set the Name to null
  };
  var data = new ASetting();
  ////When I bind control name alway null
  ////t.SetBinding(NameProperty, new Binding("Ax") { Source = data });
  //I set an error binding, it must throw NullReferenceException
  t.SetBinding(TextBox.AcceptsReturnProperty, new Binding
  {
      Source = data,
      Path = new PropertyPath("aaa")
  });
```

or binding

```csharp
public class ASetting
    {
        public string Ax { get; set; }
    }
    public partial class MainWindow : Window
    {
        public MainWindow()
        {
            InitializeComponent();
            var t = new TextBox();
            var data = new ASetting();
            //When I bind control name alway null
            t.SetBinding(NameProperty, new Binding("Ax") { Source = data });
            //I set an error binding, it must throw NullReferenceException
            t.SetBinding(TextBox.AcceptsReturnProperty, new Binding
            {
                Source = data,
                Path=new PropertyPath("aaa")
            });
        }
    }
```

`NullreferencEexception` exception will be thrown when debugging these two pieces of code in vs. `NullreferencEexception` will not be thrown when debugging these two pieces of code in vs after modifying the application

## Risk

It will change error binding message build.


